<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 06:20:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>IEA表示，氢能项目投资正在加速，但不确定性仍然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/hydrogen-project-investments-are-accelerating-uncertainty-remains-iea-says-2024-10-02/</link><description>国际能源署 (IEA) 在周三的一份报告中表示，过去 12 个月，氢项目的最终投资决定增加了一倍，其中以中国为主，但由于该行业面临不确定性，装机容量和需求较低。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 05:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/hydrogen-project-investments-are-accelerating-uncertainty-remains-iea-says-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警首次进入北极与俄罗斯联合巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-coast-guard-enters-arctic-first-time-patrol-with-russia-2024-10-02/</link><description>据官方媒体周三报道，中国海警船队首次进入北冰洋，与俄罗斯海警船队进行联合巡逻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 04:46:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-coast-guard-enters-arctic-first-time-patrol-with-russia-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>大多数亚洲股市下滑，中东风险推动油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-02/</link><description>周三，大多数亚洲股市下跌，追随华尔街的抛售潮，此前伊朗对以色列的弹道导弹袭击引发了人们对更广泛地区冲突的担忧，而原油则因供应中断的风险而走高。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 01:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾因台风“Krathon”而停电，预报有暴雨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-shuts-down-ahead-typhoon-krathons-arrival-torrential-rain-forecast-2024-10-02/</link><description>台湾周三关闭，数百架航班停飞，学校、办公室和金融市场关闭，预计台风“克拉松”即将到来，预计将带来风暴潮和暴雨袭击海岸。</description><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 00:45:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-shuts-down-ahead-typhoon-krathons-arrival-torrential-rain-forecast-2024-10-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国财政部官员称国际货币基金组织对中国政策和融资保证“过于礼貌”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/imf-too-polite-china-policies-financing-assurances-us-treasury-official-says-2024-10-01/</link><description>美国财政部一位高级官员周二表示，国际货币基金组织在批评中国经济政策时“过于客气”，应更全面地披露中国和其他一些国家为支持国际货币基金组织贷款计划而提供的融资保证。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:32:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/imf-too-polite-china-policies-financing-assurances-us-treasury-official-says-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：伊朗和以色列紧张局势引发市场下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-10-01/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 21:47:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔希拉尔击败阿尔肖塔，阿尔艾因在亚洲冠军联赛中失利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-hilal-down-al-shorta-al-ain-lose-asian-champions-league-2024-10-01/</link><description>周二，阿尔希拉尔在利雅得以 5-0 击败伊拉克的阿尔肖塔，与沙特职业联赛球队阿尔阿赫利一起在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛的两场比赛中获得最高分，卫冕冠军阿尔艾因以 4-2 输给阿尔阿赫利-加拉法。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 21:11:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-hilal-down-al-shorta-al-ain-lose-asian-champions-league-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔兹证实，天安门抗议期间他在美国，而不是亚洲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/walz-was-us-not-asia-during-tiananmen-protests-minnesota-radio-reports-2024-10-01/</link><description>民主党副总统候选人蒂姆·沃尔兹 (Tim Walz) 在 1989 年天安门广场镇压期间并不像他所说的那样在香港或亚洲，明尼苏达州公共广播电台发现了当时与他的说法相矛盾的照片和报纸报道后，他于周二晚证实了这一点。索赔。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 20:44:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/walz-was-us-not-asia-during-tiananmen-protests-minnesota-radio-reports-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>耐克撤回年度预测，暗示假日季节疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nike-posts-bigger-than-expected-quarterly-sales-drop-2024-10-01/</link><description>耐克周二撤回了年度收入预测，就在新任首席执行官即将接掌这家运动服装巨头之际，该公司正面临着可能充满折扣且其网站和移动应用程序流量疲弱的假日季节。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 20:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nike-posts-bigger-than-expected-quarterly-sales-drop-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>意大利布雷博开始出售倍耐力股份，抑制合并猜测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-brembo-starts-sale-56-pirelli-stake-2024-10-01/</link><description>布雷博周二表示，它正在开始出售其在轮胎制造商倍耐力的全部股份，价值约3亿欧元（3.32亿美元），此举平息了有关这两家意大利集团合并的猜测。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 17:22:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-brembo-starts-sale-56-pirelli-stake-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>柬埔寨表示欢迎美国海军在中国的帮助下扩大港口规模</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodia-says-it-would-welcome-us-navy-port-expanded-with-chinas-help-2024-10-01/</link><description>柬埔寨周二表示，欢迎美国海军访问其云朗海军基地，五角大楼担心该基地将成为中国的前哨基地。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 17:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodia-says-it-would-welcome-us-navy-port-expanded-with-chinas-help-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，LME 将在 2024 年底前批准香港仓储</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-approve-hong-kong-warehousing-by-end-2024-sources-say-2024-10-01/</link><description>三位知情人士表示，伦敦金属交易所（LME）将于今年年底前批准将其全球金属仓储网络扩展到香港，从而向中国大陆打开大门。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 16:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-approve-hong-kong-warehousing-by-end-2024-sources-say-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>美中谈判有助于避免中国对关税上调进行报复——财政部官员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-china-talks-helping-avoid-chinese-retaliation-against-tariff-hikes-treasury-2024-10-01/</link><description>美国财政部最高经济外交官在周二播出的采访中表示，中国没有对美国对中国进口产品提高关税进行报复，部分原因是世界最大的两个经济体之间仍在继续对话。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 15:35:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-china-talks-helping-avoid-chinese-retaliation-against-tariff-hikes-treasury-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>黄金上涨削弱了主要市场的实物需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-rally-cripples-physical-demand-key-markets-2024-10-01/</link><description>业内人士和分析师表示，随着价格持续上涨，主要市场的黄金实物需求大幅下降，一些零售消费者选择出售其持有的黄金并获利了结。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 15:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-rally-cripples-physical-demand-key-markets-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>光州队击败川崎队保持亚冠完美开局</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/gwangju-down-kawasaki-maintain-perfect-start-asian-champions-league-2024-10-01/</link><description>韩国光州足球俱乐部周二以 1-0 击败 J 联赛球队川崎前锋，在中超球队上海港队和上海申花队的苦苦挣扎中获得亚冠精英赛的背靠背胜利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 14:50:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/gwangju-down-kawasaki-maintain-perfect-start-asian-champions-league-2024-10-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>